{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"c7457a20-297a-4243-84bf-fa14406c56e4","agentId":"a59cc9f60546b8500","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"You are implementing Task 1 of the project-reader Claude Code plugin.\n\n## Context\nWe are building a Claude Code plugin called \"project-reader\" that helps analyze iOS/Python/C++/KMM projects. The plugin lives at `~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/`.\n\n## Your Task: Create plugin directory structure and plugin.json\n\nExecute these steps exactly:\n\n**Step 1: Create all subdirectories**\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/{skills/core,skills/lang,agents,commands,hooks/tests,templates}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Add .gitkeep to track empty directories**\n```bash\nfind ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader -type d -empty -exec touch {}/.gitkeep \\;\n```\n\n**Step 3: Write plugin.json**\n```bash\ncat > ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/plugin.json << 'EOF'\n{\n  \"name\": \"project-reader\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"多语言项目结构解读、源码分析与自动化辅助工具，支持 iOS/Swift/OC、Python、C++、KMM\",\n  \"author\": {\n    \"name\": \"xpeng\"\n  }\n}\nEOF\n```\n\n**Step 4: Verify directory structure**\n```bash\nfind ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader -type d | sort\n```\nExpected: should include agents, commands, hooks, hooks/tests, skills, skills/core, skills/lang, templates directories.\n\n**Step 5: Initialize git and commit**\n```bash\ncd ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader\ngit init\ngit add plugin.json $(find . -name \".gitkeep\")\ngit commit -m \"feat: init project-reader plugin skeleton with directory structure\"\n```\n\n## Reporting\nWhen done, report:\n- Status: DONE / DONE_WITH_CONCERNS / BLOCKED\n- What was created\n- Output of the directory verification\n- Git commit hash"},"uuid":"378b1f8f-48d4-4663-b6c3-f0df181d6c87","timestamp":"2026-03-17T03:39:00.699Z","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/xpeng/Desktop/AiStudy/claude-learn/plugin-dev","sessionId":"95b3d4f4-812